{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_018KSpTbKqojVYznszjBAfyw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issues:\n\n1. `/app` vhost:\n   - `ops-user` has full `.*` `.*` `.*` permissions - should NOT have any permissions on /app\n   - `app-user` has configure=\"\" (empty), write=\".*\", read=\".*\" - needs full configure/write/read (configure should be `.*`)\n\n2. `/ops` vhost:\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions - needs full configure/write/read (`.*` `.*` `.*`)\n   - No permissions at all for ops-user\n   \nSo the fix is straightforward: I need to grant `app-user` full configure permissions on `/app`, revoke `ops-user` from `/app` entirely, and give `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`. I should also verify that `app-user` doesn't have any lingering permissions on the `/ops` vhost.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":944,"cache_read_input_tokens":28781,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":944},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5781a21-f9c3-4f6f-ba42-e13869579ad1","uuid":"60851da3-3d3d-4952-b054-66efd65cef2b","request_id":"req_011CcdE5P2HzZpmTBRq3S6ho"}
